<li><a href="/wiki/Belfast" title="Belfast">Belfast</a>: −8&#160;°C (18&#160;°F)</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Madrid" title="Madrid">Madrid</a>: −8&#160;°C (18&#160;°F)</li>
